@startuml view-upcoming-dates
title View Upcoming Dates User Flow

actor User
participant "Dashboard" as Dashboard
participant "Upcoming Widget" as Widget
participant "API" as API
participant "Database" as DB

User -> Dashboard: Navigate to dashboard
Dashboard -> API: GET /api/dates/upcoming?days=30
API -> DB: Query dates within 30 days
DB --> API: Return upcoming dates
API --> Dashboard: Return date list

Dashboard -> Widget: Populate upcoming dates widget
Widget -> User: Display upcoming events\n(sorted by date)

alt User wants more details
    User -> Widget: Click on date entry
    Widget -> Dashboard: Navigate to date detail
    Dashboard -> User: Show full date details
end

alt User wants to filter
    User -> Widget: Select filter (Birthday/Anniversary)
    Widget -> API: GET /api/dates/upcoming?type={type}
    API --> Widget: Return filtered results
    Widget -> User: Display filtered dates
end

@enduml
